QuestData.Title: Of Utmost Importance
QuestData.Description: When Garrosh's zeppelin went down, so did the induction samophlange that you recovered for us in Azshara. The Alliance have it somewhere in that keep, and Krazz wants it back.$B$BThe basement of the keep would be my best guess, so start there. When you get your hands on it, bring it back to me near the eastern tower.
QuestData.CompletionText: Krazz is waitin'. Keep it moving.
QuestData.RewardText: Brilliant! Krazz will love you something mighty for bringing this one home. Good on you.
